name: Fauna Flower 06 - Anta Flower
description:
A unique South American exemplar, whose main feature is the ability to sprout the seeds it has sown. It loves to see new fruits grow near the water. Sometimes it can be associated with something or someone who is not very smart. Actually, stupid are those who don't contribute to preserve this rare and beautiful species.
You need to set aside a good amount of space if you want to have this flower in your garden, because it's the biggest one in the forest. Despite its size, it's a gentle and sweet plant.

Fauna Flowers is a collection made of animals mixed with plants in a new kind of magical possibilities. Discover this world where flowers can be a magnificent diversity of beautiful and unique creatures.
